  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nThis is at infinality time of Medalla and we have to start from block ~500000 to block ~525000 (at least) and it's not efficient to query a  block range and wait for it to be processed before querying the next one.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nWe should be able to query 1 range ahead and process the current buffered block range at the same time. This is likely the approach we'll need to apply to initial sync if it's proved to be efficient.\r\n\r\nSome code refactoring is expected due to this change.\r\n",
